%20of%20the%20Royal%20Navy's%20seven%20Astute-class%20nuclear-powered%20attack%20submarines%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Scotland.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Milligan%20-%20PA%20Images%2FPA%20Images%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Royal%20Navy%20is%20building%2012%20new%20SSN-AUKUS%20attack%20submarines.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey're%20set%20to%20replace%20the%20UK's%20Astute-class%20attack%20submarines%20by%20the%202030s.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20comes%20as%20part%20of%20the%20UK%20government's%20bid%20to%20boost%20its%20armed%20forces%20amid%20rising%20global%20threats.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20plans%20to%20build%2012%20new%20attack%20submarines%20as%20part%20of%20sweeping%20plans%20to%20boost%20the%20country's%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%C2%A0Defence%20said%20Sunday%C2%A0that%20the%20SSN-AUKUS%20vessels%20would%20be%20built%20as%20part%20of%20the%20UK's%20Strategic%20Review%20to%20enhance%20its%20military%20strength%20amid%20rising%20global%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey'll%20be%20deployed%20as%20part%20of%20the%20AUKUS%20alliance%20between%20the%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20the%20US%2C%20with%20the%20submarines%20having%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcommonslibrary.parliament.uk%2Fresearch-briefings%2Fcbp-9843%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAUKUS%2520is%2520a%2520defence%2520and%2Cthe%2520UK%2527s%2520other%2520submarine%2520programmes%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeveloped%20alongside%20the%20Australian%20navy.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20outstanding%20submariners%20patrol%2024%2F7%20to%20keep%20us%20and%20our%20allies%20safe%2C%20but%20we%20know%20that%20threats%20are%20increasing%20and%20we%20must%20act%20decisively%20to%20face%20down%20Russian%20aggression%2C%26quot%3B%20UK%20Defence%20Secretary%20John%20Healey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWith%20new%20state-of-the-art%20submarines%20patrolling%20international%20waters%20and%20our%20own%20n