%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22smart%20balance%20spread%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20bread%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F639358b3d089dd0019bbe0c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20softens%20as%20it%20comes%20to%20room%20temperature%2C%20but%20that%20defeats%20the%20purpose%20of%20a%20buttery%20spread.%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20dark%20beige%20like%20Earth%20Balance%2C%20but%20Smart%20Balance's%20butter%20alternative%20was%20similarly%20difficult%20to%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20tried%20putting%20it%20on%20bread%2C%20it%20started%20tearing%20up%20the%20piece.%20It%20also%20came%20out%20of%20the%20container%20in%20solid%20chunks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20softened%20up%20somewhat%20as%20it%20came%20to%20room%20temperature%2C%20and%20the%20label%20at%20least%20warned%20that%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bfirm%20out%20of%20refrigeration.%26quot%3B%20But%20I%20think%20the%20perk%20of%20a%20buttery%20spread%20is%20that%20it%20can%20be%20used%20right%20out%20of%20the%20chilled%20container%2C%20unlike%20waiting%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbutter-taste-test-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal%20butter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20soften.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20flavor%2C%20Smart%20Balance%20had%20a%20great%20butter-like%20taste%20at%20first.%20But%20then%2C%20as%20it%20melted%20in%20my%20mouth%2C%20it%20left%20an%20aftertaste%20I%20didn't%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECountry%20Crock%20was%20my%20favorite%2C%20but%20I%20still%20plan%20to%20stick%20to%20traditional%20butter.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222764%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22five%20buttery%20spread%20lined%20up%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63b468ce0e1a1b00195ee89d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222073%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECountry%20Crock%20