i%3EThe%20new%20features%20transform%20the%20tools%20from%20simple%20chatbots%20into%20more%20proactive%20assistants.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESarah%20Franklin%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Lattice%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20embracing%20AI%20now%20would%20help%20protect%20jobs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hiring-white-collar-recession-jobs-tech-new-data-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ealready%20entering%20the%20workplace%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20how%20should%20employees%20make%20sure%20it%20doesn't%20take%20their%20jobs%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20HR%20software%20company%20Lattice%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20to%20embrace%20it%20now%20and%20get%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Flattice-debuts-ai-agent-for-hr-as-hris-customer-growth-surges-250-302403895.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20was%20launching%20an%20AI%20agent%20designed%20to%20help%20HR%20teams.%20The%20agent%20would%20effectively%20give%20employees%20a%20digital%20copilot%20to%20answer%20questions%20about%20payroll%2C%20benefits%2C%20and%20other%20things%20they%20might%20usually%20message%20a%20human%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Lattice%20announced%20it's%20rolling%20out%20more%20features%20to%20transform%20these%20tools%20from%20simple%20chatbots%20into%20more%20proactive%20assistants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey'll%20sit%20in%20on%201%3A1%20meetings%20with%20your%20manager.%20They'll%20nudge%20you%20if%20they%20think%20an%20employee%20is%20disengaged%20and%20at%20risk%20of%20leaving%20the%20company.%20They'll%20let%20you%20practice%20difficult%20questions%20before%20having%20them%20with%20other%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Lattice%20is%20applying%20those%20same%20techniques%20to%20other%20business%20departments%20beyond%20HR%2C%20with%20what%20it's%20calling%20an%20%26quot%3Bagent%20platform.%26quot%3B%20Lattice%20CEO%20Sarah%20Franklin%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20IT%20and%20finance%20are%20two%20areas%20where%20these%20agents%20could%20be%20most%20helpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20an%20executive%20assistant%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20company%2C%20but%20my%20regular%20line%20engineer%20does%20not%20have%20an%20executive%20assistant%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Franklin.%20Lattice's%20proposal%20is%3A%20what%20if%20they%20did%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20agents%20are%20a%20big%20theme%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%20right%20now.%20As%20the%20underlying%20AI%20models%20continue%20to%20improve%20rapidly%2C%20generative%20AI%20tools%20that%20can%20actually%20carry%20out%20helpful%20tasks%20and%20act%20more%20proactively%20are%20becoming%20more%20of%20a%20reality.%20But%20Franklin%20says%20many%20companies%20are%20struggling%20to%20make%20that%20leap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20stuck%20at%20the%20starting%20line%20of%2C%20'how%20do%20I%20get%20this%20going%20for%20my%20employees%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20having%20a%20ChatGPT%20window%3F'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286519a48-e4d9-4767-a8df-2900c4e9e8ba%5C%22%3EThe%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Franklin%20says%20Lattice%20is%20trying%20to%20get%20AI%20to%20enhance%20employees%2C%20rather%20than%20find%20ways%20of%20replacing%20them%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hiring-white-collar-recession-jobs-tech-new-data-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplenty%20of%20companies%20are%20trying%20to%20get%20AI%20to%20take%20on%20white-collar%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFranklin%20believes%20using%20AI%20to%20replace%20repetitive%20daily%20manual%20tasks%2C%20such%20as%20answering%20employee%20questions%20about%20payroll%20or%20health%20insurance%20plans%2C%20will%20free%20employees%20up%20for%20more%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%26quot%3B%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20doesn't%20deny%20that%20some%20companies%20will%20look%20to%20use%20these%20AI%20tools%20to%20replace%20some%20humans%2C%20but%20she%20also%20said%20that's%20not%20what%20Lattice%20is%20trying%20to%20do.%20Instead%2C%20she%20sees%20the%20ability%20to%20offload%20menial%20tasks%20to%20AI%20as%20a%20way%20to%20make%20employees%20more%20productive%20and%20useful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20able%20to%20have%20people%20focused%20on%20the%20things%20that%20are%20really%20important%20because%20they're%20too%20busy%20doing%20the%20stuff%20that%20is%20logistical%20and%20not%20strategic%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFranklin%20says%20there%20will%20always%20be%20a%20human%20in%20the%20loop%20and%20that%20Lattice's%20AI%20agents%20won't%20act%20on%20their%20%26quot%3Bproactive%26quot%3B%20recommendations%2C%20such%20as%20contacting%20an%20employee%20who%20has%20missed%20a%20deadline%2C%20without%20a%20warm%20body%20giving%20the%20OK.%20Some%20companies%20that%20were%20bullish%20on%20AI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-05-08%2Fklarna-turns-from-ai-to-real-person-customer-service%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuch%20as%20Klarna%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20about-turned%20in%20recent%20months%20after%20discovering%20that%20taking%20humans%20out%20of%20the%20loop%20backfired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20sign%20of%20just%20how%20unchartered%20these%20waters%20are.%20Lattice%20itself%20knows%3A%20jump%20back%2010%20months%2C%20and%20the%20company%20found%20itself%20in%20a%20media%20storm%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fsarahfranklin_today-lattice-makes-history-and-leads-the-activity-7216472651043676160-_tyR%2F%3Futm_source%3Dcombined_share_message%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannouncing%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20new%20tool%20to%20let%20companies%20onboard%20AI%20%26quot%3Bemployees%26quot%3B%20and%20even%20give%20them%20official%20employment%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20go%20over%20well%2C%20and%20Lattice%20later%20walked%20back%20the%20release%2C%20but%20Franklin%20still%20believes%20the%20idea%20at%20heart%20was%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20treat%20them%20as%20employees%20that%20aren't%20ghosts%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20That%20means%20holding%20AI%20agents%20to%20the%20same%20standards%20as%20human%20employees%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20security%2C%20compliance%2C%20and%20performance%2C%20she%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20we%20have%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20how%20these%20entities%20are%20behaving.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20she%20said%2C%20will%20be%20important%20to%20preventing%20AI%20from%20just%20taking%20human%20jobs%20outright.%20It's%20an%20optimistic%20take%2C%20and%20it%20might%20prove%20to%20be%20correct.%20But%20there's%20also%20fear%20right%20now%20that%20AI%20agents%20will%20soon%20be%20good%20enough%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-warning-ai-could-eliminate-jobs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eto%20wipe%20out%20many%20white-collar%20jobs.%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20they%20are%20already%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20fear%2C%20uncertainty%2C%20doubt%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20why%20the%20time%20is%20now%20where%20we%20must%20all%20go%20through%20this%20change%20management%2C%20know%20how%20to%20be%20proficient%2C%20fluent%2C%20and%20elevated%20with%20AI%20so%20we're%20not%20replaceable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Franklin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20prevent%20this%20by%20being%20proactive%2C%20by%20seeing%20the%20future%20and%20getting%20to%20it%20first.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20something%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahlangley%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehlangley%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%