C%20CTO%20and%20VP%20of%20engineering%3B%20Ronak%20Desai%2C%20CEO%3B%20and%20Ananda%20Rajagopal%2C%20chief%20product%20officer.%3Cp%3ECiroos%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECiroos%20builds%20AI%20agents%20that%20act%20as%20site%20reliability%20teammates%20to%20find%20and%20fix%20software%20errors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20startup%20just%20launched%20from%20stealth%20with%20%2421%20million%20in%20seed%20funding%20from%20Energy%20Impact%20Partners.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20got%20an%20exclusive%20look%20at%20the%20pitch%20deck%20Ciroos%20used%20to%20raise%20its%20seed%20round.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20enterprise%20tech%20veterans%20just%20raised%20%2421%20million%20to%20introduce%20an%20AI%20fix%20to%20some%20of%20the%20most%20painful%20software%20engineering%20problems%3A%20middle-of-the-night%20outages%20and%20other%20critical%20system%20failures%20that%20require%20immediate%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiroos%2C%20a%20new%20startup%20founded%20by%20former%20Cisco%2C%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20and%20Gigamon%20executives%2C%20just%20launched%20from%20stealth%20with%20its%20seed%20funding%20round%2C%20led%20by%20Energy%20Impact%20Partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeadquartered%20in%20Pleasanton%2C%20California%2C%20Ciroos%20builds%20AI%20agents%20that%20act%20as%20site%20reliability%20engineering%20(SRE)%20teammates.%20Traditionally%2C%20it%20can%20take%20a%20long%20time%20and%20many%20people%20to%20keep%20software%20systems%20running%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20find%20a%20fix%20when%20something%20breaks.%20When%20a%20website%20breaks%20down%20overnight%20or%20during%20a%20holiday%20weekend%2C%20it's%20up%20to%20a%20team%20of%20unlucky%2C%20on-call%20engineers%20in%20triage%20mode%20to%20find%20a%20fix%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiroos's%20agents%20work%20alongside%20a%20company's%20operations%20team%20to%20detect%20problems%20before%20a%20human%20is%20officially%20alerted%2C%20identify%20the%20root%20cause%2C%20and%20either%20fix%20them%20autonomously%20or%20help%20their%20human%20teammates%20fix%20them%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsidering%20that%20the%20median%20size%20of%20a%20seed%20funding%20round%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202024%20was%20just%20%241.3%20million%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.crunchbase.com%2Fventure%2Fus-median-round-size-growing-h1-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20Crunchbase%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ciroos's%20%2421%20million%20round%20is%20staggering%20in%20comparison.%20The%20startup's%20CEO%2C%20Ronak%20Desai%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20and%20his%20co-founders%20connected%20with%20investors%20who%20agreed%20that%20enterprise%20operations%20needed%20a%20new%20approach%2C%20which%20AI%20agents%20could%20achieve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20deep%20curiosity%20from%20investors%20on%20the%20customer%20anecdotes%20we%20shared%2C%20and%20everybody%20noted%20our%20focus%20on%20cross-domain%20correlation%20as%20our%20point%20of%20differentiation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BInvestors%20also%20readily%20recognized%20our%20execution%20track%20record%2C%20our%20relentless%20customer%20focus%2C%20and%20the%20deep%20experience%20we%20had%20assembled%20%E2%80%94%20all%20necessary%20ingredients%20to%20build%20enterprise-class%20products.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesai%20said%20that%20with%20its%20funding%20round%20completed%2C%20Ciroos%20will%20focus%20on%20hiring%3A%20the%20startup%20plans%20to%20staff%20up%20with%20AI%20engineers%2C%20full-stack%20engineers%2C%20and%20salespeople%20in%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20Area%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20agents%20are%20booming%20in%202025%2C%20and%20Ciroos%20faces%20stiff%20competition%20from%20a%20multitude%20of%20enterprise%20tech%20startups%20that%20build%20AI%20teammates%20to%20help%20software%20and%20computer%20engineers.%20%3Cspan%3EIn%20May%2C%20no-code%20AI%20agent%20startup%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http