0goods%20that%20I%20thought%20I%20could%20decorate%20my%20entire%20apartment%20with%20its%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20wasn't%20expecting%20the%20tech%20neighborhood%20to%20be%20so%20full%20of%20nature.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Geese%20and%20people%20wander%20around%20a%20park%20in%20front%20of%20office%20buildings%2C%20including%20a%20Google%20building%20with%20trees%20on%20the%20roof%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f83de6ffb6822ec614827%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Google%20building%20sits%20behind%20a%20park%20in%20South%20Lake%20Union.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESeattle%20has%20long%20been%20known%20as%20a%20tech%20hub%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincredibly-lonely-high-paying-tech-job-seattle-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineers%20move%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20droves%20to%20work%20at%20big%20companies%20like%20Amazon%20and%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocals%20told%20me%20I%20could%20find%20the%20booming%20scene%20in%20the%20South%20Lake%20Union%20neighborhood%2C%20home%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-headquarters%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20Amazon%20headquarters%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20company's%20presence%20in%20more%20than%2030%20office%20buildings%20led%20to%20the%20neighborhood's%20nickname%2C%20%26quot%3BAmazonia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20visiting%2C%20I%20expected%20to%20find%20nothing%20but%20business-centric%20streets%20lined%20with%20glass%20skyscrapers%20in%20a%20tech-fueled%20neighborhood.%20So%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20the%20large%20presence%20of%20nature%20in%20South%20Lake%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20neighborhood%20borders%20Lake%20Union%2C%20where%20I%20explored%20a%20waterfront%20park%20filled%20with%20runners%2C%20bic