he%20phrase%20micro-dosing%20happiness.%20It's%20about%20creating%20happy%20moments%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20thought%20of%20happiness%20as%20a%20practice%2C%20but%20the%20more%20I%20sought%20out%20and%20focused%20on%20those%20small%20microdosing%20moments%2C%20the%20better%20it%20made%20me%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222516bad7-e3f6-4224-b8ed-b05b00b46c93%5C%22%3EThe%20biggest%20surprise%20of%20the%20whole%20retreat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hiking%20is%20what%20attracted%20me%20to%20the%20program%2C%20initially%2C%20and%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20surprise%20of%20the%20whole%20retreat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHiking%20is%20my%20happy%20place%3A%20I've%20hiked%20the%20Inca%20Trail%20in%20Peru%20and%20trekked%20through%20Patagonia%20in%20Chile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20we%20were%20told%20they%20divided%20hiking%20groups%20into%20four%20categories%20(1-4%2C%20fastest%20to%20slowest)%2C%20I%20figured%20I'd%20fall%20into%20group%202%2C%20given%20my%20recent%20surgery%20and%20weight%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20huge%20wake-up%20call%20(and%20a%20hit%20to%20my%20ego)%20to%20find%20out%20I%20had%20to%20fall%20behind%20to%20group%204%2C%20the%20slowest.%20Turns%20out%2C%20group%204%20was%20fabulous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20we%20hiked%20slower%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20take%20in%20the%20beautiful%20flowers%2C%20frogs%2C%20deer%2C%20and%20other%20wildlife%20while%20the%20women%20and%20I%20bonded%20over%20our%20various%20life%20struggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20to%20accept%20%E2%80%94%20and%20appreciate%20%E2%80%94%20the%20slower%20pace.%20And%20the%20connections%20I%20made%20with%20those%20women%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20people%20at%20the%20retreat%20(there%20were%2013%20of%20us%2C%20three%20men%20and%20ten%20women%3B%20Mountain%20Trek%20limits%20it%20to%2016%20total)%2C%20were%20one%20of%20the%20best%20parts%20of%20that%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22509320a8-a9eb-4cd1-8767-416737cd2dd6%5C%22%3EMy%20week%20in%20the%20mountains%20was%20the%20perfect%20reset%20I%20needed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20home%2C%20I'm%20still%20seeing%20the%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20rediscovered%20my%20motivation%20to%20move%20and%20am%20committed%20to%20the%20gym%20five%20days%20a%20week%2C%20walking%20with%20a%20friend%20three%20to%20four%20times%20a%20week%2C%20and%20sitting%20less%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20break%20up%20my%20day%20with%20movement%20breaks%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20just%20going%20up%20and%20down%20the%20stairs%20for%20five%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20finally%20curbed%20my%20overeating%20habit.%20The%20retreat%20offered%20six%20small%20meals%20a%20day%20without%20second%20servings.%20I%20was%20hungry%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20but%20my%20body%20adapted%20after%20that%2C%20and%20I've%20kept%20my%20portion%20sizes%20smaller%20at%20home%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20routine%20makes%20me%20feel%20more%20energized%20and%20less%20stressed.%20It's%20largely%20thanks%20to%20the%20retreat%20and%20admitting%20to%20myself%20that%20I%20needed%20a%20break%2C%20and%20being%20brave%20enough%20to%20take%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20met%20several%20people%20on%20the%20retreat%20who%20were%20regulars%2C%20and%20I%20could%20see%20myself%20going%20back.%20I%20missed%20my%20husband%20and%20kids%2C%20but%20to%20spend%20a%20full%20week%20really%20working%20on%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20emotionally%2C%20physically%2C%20mentally%20%E2%80%94%20was%20a%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspent-6900-week-retreat-perfect-mental-physical-reset-i-needed-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748945701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683db8d06ffb6822ec61e202%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspent-6900-week-retreat-perfect-mental-physical-reset-