0surgery%2C%20radiation%20therapy%2C%20and%20hormone%20therapy%20to%20turn%20off%20testosterone%20production%20in%20my%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20surgery%20in%20July%202021%2C%20after%20which%20I%20had%20issues%20with%20incontinence.%20Despite%20physical%20therapy%20to%20improve%20it%2C%20I%20never%20regained%20full%20control%20of%20my%20bladder.%20This%20made%20the%20radiation%20therapy%2C%20which%20came%20about%20five-and-a-half%20months%20later%2C%20very%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20time%2C%20I%20had%20to%20come%20in%20with%20an%20empty%20rectum%20and%20a%20full%20bladder.%20The%20full%20bladder%20basically%20pushes%20the%20rectum%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20as%20much%20in%20the%20field%20where%20they're%20going%20to%20shoot%20with%20radiation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20the%2039%20radiation%20sessions%20I%20completed%20only%20lasts%20about%2015%20minutes%2C%20but%20I%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20getting%20my%20bladder%20full%20enough%20and%20then%20holding%20it%20long%20enough%20for%20the%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20through%20it%2C%20I'd%20play%20a%20game%20with%20myself%3A%20They%20had%20music%20going%2C%20and%20I%20would%20just%20listen%20to%20the%20music%20and%20try%20to%20memorize%20it.%20Then%2C%20I%20went%20on%20Facebook%20afterward%20and%20posted%20a%20list%20of%20all%20the%20songs%20%E2%80%94%20it%20became%20my%20%26quot%3BPlaylist%20of%20the%20day%26quot%3B%20for%20friends%20and%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20androgen%20deprivation%20therapy%2C%20aka%20hormone%20therapy%2C%20was%20a%20shot%20that%20I%20got%20every%20three%20months%2C%20along%20with%20pills%20that%20I%20was%20taking%20every%20day.%20I%20did%20this%20therapy%20for%20about%2024%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20side%20effects%20were%20pretty%20harsh.%20I%20experienced%20hot%20flashes%2C%20mood%20swings%2C%20additional%20abdominal%20fat%2C%20loss%20of%20muscle%20mass%20and%20bone%20density%2C%20and%20it%20killed%20my%20libido.%20I%20got%20back%20into%20lifting%20weight