ech%20Week%20kickoff%20power%20walk%20posed%20for%20a%20photo.%3Cp%3EAlice%20Tecotzky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20talked%20to%20founders%20at%20a%20Tech%20Week%20event%20in%20New%20York%20and%20most%20of%20them%20were%20working%20in%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20their%20excitement%20about%20AI%2C%20they%20all%20said%20there's%20a%20key%20skill%20the%20bots%20don't%20have.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20I%20felt%20after%20all%20of%20the%20AI%20talk%3A%20connected%20to%20other%20human%20beings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20officially%20Tech%20Week%20in%20New%20York%2C%20when%20the%20city%20cosplays%20as%20San%20Francisco%20and%20networking%20happy%20hours%20take%20over%20seemingly%20every%20bar.%20On%20Sunday%20evening%2C%20around%2050%20founders%20and%20investors%20kicked%20off%20the%20week%20with%20a%20power%20walk%20on%20the%20High%20Line%20%E2%80%94%20and%20while%20pretty%20much%20everyone%20seemed%20to%20be%20discussing%20AI%2C%20they%20told%20me%20that%20the%20event%20itself%20represented%20what%20new%20technology%20can't%20replace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20arrived%20at%20the%20walk%20a%20few%20minutes%20early%20to%20find%20a%20small%20crowd%20assembled%2C%20the%20brave%20wearing%20athletic%20shorts%20in%20the%20uncharacteristically%20cold%20June%20weather.%20As%20we%20started%20to%20walk%2C%20the%20word%20'AI'%20seemed%20to%20dot%20every%20conversation%20I%20overheard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20six%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efounders%20I%20talked%20to%2C%20five%20of%20them%20explicitly%20marketed%20their%20projects%20as%20AI%20companies.%20All%20of%20the%20AI%20enthusiasts%20I%20talked%20to%2C%20though%2C%20independently%20told%20me%20there's%20one%20crucial%20business%20skill%20that%20the%20technology%20can't%20master%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-skill-important-coding-empathy-engineer-peter-schwartz-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterpe