kers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwiss-made%20brands%20are%20shipping%20more%20watches%20to%20the%20US%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20the%20tariff%2C%20which%20is%20paused%20until%20July.%20Exports%20from%20Switzerland%20to%20the%20US%20were%20up%20149.2%25%20year-over-year%20in%20April%2C%20when%20tariffs%20were%20announced%2C%20the%20Federation%20of%20the%20Swiss%20Watch%20industry%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fhs.swiss%2Feng%2Fstatistics.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaplan%20is%20more%20worried%20about%20the%20impact%20on%20watch%20sellers%20than%20buyers.%20Bob's%20Watches%20buys%20watches%20from%20sellers%20and%20lists%20them%20on%20its%20website.%20Sellers%20may%20want%20to%20be%20paid%20more%20for%20their%20pre-owned%20watches%20if%20retail%20prices%20for%20similar%20models%20are%20spiking%20due%20to%20tariffs.%20Kaplan%20said%20his%20company%20may%20have%20to%20revisit%20how%20it%20negotiates%20prices%20if%20complaints%20from%20sellers%20become%20widespread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20operates%20internationally%2C%20but%20sellers%20outside%20the%20US%20don't%20make%20up%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20its%20business%2C%20Kaplan%20said.%20The%20company%20charges%20a%20%24150%20shipping%20fee%20for%20orders%20from%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaplan%20has%20been%20at%20Bob's%20Watches%20for%20six%20years%20and%20in%20the%20Swiss%20watch%20industry%20for%2027%20years.%20He's%20worked%20at%20brands%20like%20Movado%2C%20Fendi%2C%20and%20Swatch%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20business%20has%20grown%20recently%20in%20part%20because%20of%20younger%20buyers.%20They%20aren't%20as%20interested%20in%20the%20%24300%20to%20%24500%20watches%20they%20can%20purchase%20at%20a%20department%20store.%20Luxury%20watches%20are%20an%20asset%20that%20can%20appreciate%20in%20value%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20style%20and%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20their%20eyes%20on%20something%20for%20the%20future%20because%20they%20now%20understand%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaplan%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20educated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpre-owned-watch-sales-bobs-watches-increase-as-tariffs-loom-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748943182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6839fa5dc6ad288d14823fe3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpre-owned-watch-sales-bobs-watches-increase-as-tariffs-loom-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pre-owned%20watch%20marketplace%20Bob's%20Watches%20is%20seeing%20a%20sales%20bump%20as%20tariffs%20loom%20and%20luxury%20brands%20hike%20prices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpre-owned-watch-sales-bobs-watches-increase-as-tariffs-loom-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Maalik%E2%80%99%20teaser%3A%20Rajkummar%20Rao%20in%20his%20darkest%20avatar%20yet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748943175000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121594143%2Cimgsize-24038.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmaalik-teaser-rajkummar-rao-unleashes-his-darkest-avatar-yet-in-gritty-gangster-drama%2Farticleshow%2F121594151.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F121594151.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERajkummar%20Rao's%20menacing%20transformation%20in%20the%20'Maalik'%20teaser%20has%20set%20the%20internet%20ablaze.%20Directed%20by%20Pulkit%20and%20set%20in%201988%20Allahabad%2C%20the%20film%20plunges%20viewers%20into%20a%20gritty%20underworld%20of%20blood%2C%